{"tid":131686,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以色列大使館 有冇觸犯辱警罪?","createTime":"2017-02-23T08:42:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T08:53:21.000Z","uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ae807d457b582bc41b0541e73821a30be5cf78c","tid":131686,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:42:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc85631094747ae02ad036e615797ccd62e6589f","tid":131686,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:43:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc4f01408571e4e40f530a9b149c09d477d0974","tid":131686,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:44:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170223/large/1487834389_8a35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170223%2Flarge%2F1487834389_8a35.jpg&h=d50a0468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港猶太大屠殺及寬容中心教育總監李家豪，對於有警員自比「被納粹德軍逼害的猶太人」感詫異，認為反映對這場歷史浩劫不了解、欠尊重。他指出，第二次世界大戰中，一共超過600萬名猶太人被屠殺，而逼害猶太人的乃有系統、有國家在背後支持的政權，屠殺手段包括送到「滅絕營」中，利用毒氣室等手段殺害，質疑發言警員所指被「納粹德軍」逼害，跟史實有何可類比之處，以及「納粹德軍」在現實中代表何方、何人。<br />\n<br />\n李家豪指，今早得悉居港的猶太人社群，對相關警員言論有反響，主要是感到詫異。他表示難以代表社群回答有否覺得不受尊重，惟有一點可以肯定，就是猶太人要求尊重史實，盼望國際了解他們被逼害的事實。<br />\n<br />\n李又分享指，昨晚看到新聞片段時，正值他製作關於大屠殺的教材，最令他感驚詫的，是發言者詢問同僚是否認同有如猶太人般被逼害時，台下竟「一呼百應」。<br />\n<br />\n李家豪續指，該中心每年舉辦多項公眾教育活動，包括到大學、中學及國際學校演講，亦會舉辦相關電影節，以及每年邀請僅餘的大屠殺倖存者來港分享。他表示，大部分活動均對公眾開放，歡迎任何人包括警方參與。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚4個警察協會集會期間，有警員上台發言時表示，「我形容就係我咃依家就係第二次世界大戰，我哋係猶太人，我哋被迫害緊，被德國納粹軍隊迫害緊我哋猶太人呀，啱唔啱呀」，全場即回答「係！」</blockquote>"},{"pid":"0bc65f29b6fcf4aa1a3ae81152de3c83b26d41f0","tid":131686,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:47:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最令他感驚詫的，是發言者詢問同僚是否認同有如猶太人般被逼害時，台下竟「一呼百應」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n辱警罪要立即立法! 小國使館竟然反對呀蛇言論<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850bf40f246c8180c6ef17e185ec1653ced24699","tid":131686,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:49:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6fa62a5148a276ade63b1ba78914680c5e1b18","tid":131686,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:49:29.000Z","msg":"人地有外交豁免權<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b638059315e95023a2539c405d5295c66f764341","tid":131686,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:50:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地有外交豁免權<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n龍門可以搬架啫"},{"pid":"a34916def842908d9ffa82bea8cf6ac7ff381ecd","tid":131686,"uid":12404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:50:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地有外交豁免權<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呀蛇做嘢唔使你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac1924ed1d5ea7490a8fd89b48d98faf44c3387","tid":131686,"uid":57460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:50:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地有外交豁免權<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n外交豁免權都要企埋一邊呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母！</span></span>"},{"pid":"fbae8fc3915f14d4fef9df13aec6ad61883893d2","tid":131686,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:50:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地有外交豁免權<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n黑犬都唔想守法律,阿sir